Feature: Demopencart functionality
Scenario: Click on ShowLaptops link
Given If user is on Main page
When Mouse hover on Laptops And Notebooks
And Click on Show All Laptops And Notebooks
Then verify Laptop And Notebook size

Scenario: Click on FirstLaptops image
Given If user is on Laptops and Notebooks
When Click on FirstLaptop image
And Click on Add To Cart
Then verify success message.